high_descs: Turn around and cross the room, then go to your right, to the end table at the left end of the sofa.
Pick up the remote control wand that is in front of the lamp, to the left of the keys.
Turn around and cross the room to the far wall, then go left until you reach the corner chair.
Put the control wand halfway between the cardboard box and the front edge of the chair seat, parallel to the edge.
Turn around and retrace your path to the sofa end table.
Pick up the remote control wand from the end table.
Take the control wand to the corner chair where the first wand now is.
Place the wand end-to-end with the first wand, parallel with the front edge of the chair seat.
